<html>
<head>
  <title>Space Serveurs - Tous les serveurs</title>
<%- include('../blocks/header') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../blocks/navbar', { bot, user }) %>
  <div class="bigthingy row">
  <div class="seeme col-md-8 offset-md-2 row">
    <div class="seeme col-sm-2 sinfo">
      <p id="bigytxt" class="bigyimg" style="font-size:88px;"><i class="fas fa-server"></i></p>
    </div>
    <div class="seeme col-sm-10 sinfo">
      <p id="bigytxt"><span style="font-size:25px; font-weight:bold;">Tous les serveurs</span><br />Vous trouverez ci-dessous une liste des serveurs auxquels le bot a accès.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <br />  <br />  <br />
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
  <% if (cards.length === 0) { %>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-block">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="https://discord.mx/da7qc.png" width="50px" style="width:128px; height:128px; background-color:#F6F6F6; border-radius:50%;" alt="">
          <h4 class="card-title">Pas de serveurs</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Le bot n'a pas de serveurs.</p>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
            <% } else { %>
              <% for(let i of cards) { %>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
    <div class="card">
    <div class="card-block">
      <% if (bot.guilds.cache.get(i.guildid).icon) { %>
        <img class="card-img-top" src="<%= `${bot.guilds.cache.get(i.guildid).iconURL({format: 'png', size: 128 })}` %>" width="50px" style="width:128px; height:128px; background-color:#F6F6F6; border-radius:50%;" alt="">
      <% } else { %>
        <canvas class="card-img-top" id="<%= bot.guilds.cache.get(i.guildid).name.split(' ').join('').replace(`'`, ``) %>" width="50px" style="width:128px; height:128px; background-color:#7289da; border-radius:50%;" height="50px"></canvas>
        <script>
          function draw() {
            const ctx = document.getElementById("<%= bot.guilds.cache.get(i.guildid).name.split(' ').join('').replace(`'`, ``) %>").getContext('2d');
            ctx.font = '20px Arial';
            ctx.textAlign = "center";
            ctx.fillStyle = "white";
            ctx.fillText("<%= bot.guilds.cache.get(i.guildid).name.split(' ').map(v => v[0]).join('') %>", 25, 33);
          };
          draw();
        </script>
      <% } %>
      <h4 class="card-title"><%= bot.guilds.cache.get(i.guildid).name %></h4>
      <p class="card-text"><%= i.description.length > 55 ? `${i.description.slice(0,55)}...` : i.description %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
      <a class="btn btn-info btn-sm btn-block" href="/server/<%= i.guildid %>/" role="button">Voir la page</a>
      <div class="btn-group btn-block">
        <a class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary" style="width:50%;max-width:50%;" href="/server/<%= i.guildid %>/edit">Éditer</a>
        <a class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" style="width:50%;max-width:50%;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#delModal" data-guildid="<%= i.guildid %>">Supprimer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
    <% } %>
  <% } %>
  </div>
  </div><br /><br />
  <div class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="delModal">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title">Es-tu sûr?</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>Êtes-vous sûr de vouloir supprimer la guilde avec l'identifiant de <code id="delmsg"></code>?<br/><br/>Cette action est <strong style="color:red;">IRRÉVERSIBLE</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Fermer</button>
          <a id="delbtn" href="/me/admin?error=no-id-set" class="btn btn-danger">Supprimer</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('../blocks/footer') %>
  <script>
  $('#delModal').on('show.bs.modal', function (event) {
    var guildId = $(event.relatedTarget).data('guildid');
    $(this).find('#delmsg').text(guildId);
    $(this).find('#delbtn').attr('href', `/server/${guildId}/delete`);
  })
  </script>
</body>
<style>
  a {
 -webkit-transition: .25s all;
 transition: .25s all;
}
.card {
  padding-left:auto;
  padding-right:auto;
  min-height:360px;
  margin-top:15px;
 box-shadow: 0 2px 5px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16), 0 2px 10px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
 -webkit-transition: .25s box-shadow;
 transition: .25s;
 background: #FEFEFE;
 top:0;
}
.card:focus, .card:hover {
 box-shadow: 0 5px 11px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18), 0 4px 15px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
 top:-1px;
}
.card-inverse .card-img-overlay {
 background-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.85);
 border-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.85);
}
.card-img-top{
  margin-top:10px;
}
.col-xs-12{
  text-align:center;
  margin-left:auto;
  margin-right:auto;
}
.row{
  margin-left:auto;
  margin-right:auto;
}
.card-footer {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
bottom: 0px;
}
</style>
</html>
